{"tid":1416891,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知唔知咩叫不割蓆？","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:46:52.000Z","uid":262035,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6778c5d17bd357d6132589de5289b35c7d44fe","tid":1416891,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆</span></span><br />\n姐係無論如何都同對方坐同一條船<br />\n要俾人鬧就一齊受<br />\n共同進退<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但咁樣唔代表唔可以反省批評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">正正大家有共同目標坐同一條船<br />\n先想俾下意見點樣可以做得更好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽到唔同意見<br />\n不妨諗下對方有冇道理<br />\n有既話諗下點改善<br />\n冇既話諗下咩原因同點反駁<br />\n大家好言相對理性討論<br />\n<br />\n我地絕對無任何內鬥既本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf5c16e836b2c04313c791987d7b9c0bbc9514","tid":1416891,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"514d7d51d8371b65f201314e2d48ebb940d75fac","tid":1416891,"uid":292173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e162f0a19038769421920f7433db50397966eb9f","tid":1416891,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"香港示威者已經好冷靜克制 唔好自己嚇自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a970448975564530fa44e484145f7a95996f88d2","tid":1416891,"uid":297811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"點都不割蓆，永遠撐前線！！！！！"},{"pid":"9ba1dd0f8674697f9780c68d3350b0eb69cb23b0","tid":1416891,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"用腦！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"b623745c96722d610b2ff8e28ab73a65ee8c912b","tid":141